<br>
This argument was had over and over again when it first happened.  How bout we stop arguing over it and move on to the next possible dynamic mob?<br>
<br>
<br>
&lt;note added&gt; I wasn't responding here to the original question.  It was some of the more hostile responses it got that kicked up my feelings on it.<br>
